						<summary>

						<p>This is damaged and the beginning is lost. It has no date and refers to the [Noḻamba]-Pallava king <hi rend="bold">Mayindamma</hi> (Mahēndravarman I) and • • <hi rend="bold">ḻambādhirāja</hi> and records the grant of some land to a <hi rend="italic">basadi</hi> and for the feeding of <hi rend="italic">tapasvins.</hi> Palaeographically the record may be placed in the 9th century A.D. </p>						

						</summary>
